{"word":"H3243 - יָנַק - yânaq - yaw-nak' - Milch","slug":"H3243","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָנַק</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yânaq"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-nak'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Milch"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05E0;&#x05E7; - ya&#x0302;naq</b> - <i>yaw-nak'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>suck</i>; causatively to <i>give milk: - </i>milch, nurse (-ing mother), give, make to) suck (-ing child, -ling)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3126\">H3126</a>, <a href=\"#/H3127\">H3127</a>, <a href=\"#/H3242\">H3242</a>"}]}